import './App.css';
import { ChakraProvider,Box ,Container,Flex,CSSReset,GridItem,Grid} from '@chakra-ui/react'
import { } from '@chakra-ui/icons'
import Navbar from './components/navBar';
import SideBar from './components/leftSideBar';


function App() {
  return (
    <ChakraProvider>
      <CSSReset />
      <Flex direction="column" height="100vh">
        <Navbar />
        <Flex flex="1">
          {/* Adjust the Box styling as needed */}
          <Box
            mx="2"
            my="2"
            width="100%"
            
            align="center"
            justify="center"
          >
            <Grid templateColumns="15% 60% 25%" gap='1' h="100%" w='98%'>
              <GridItem colSpan={1} borderLeftRadius='20' bgColor="red" >
                Column 1
              </GridItem>
              <GridItem colSpan={1}  bgColor="red">
                Column 2
              </GridItem>
              <GridItem colSpan={1} borderRightRadius='20' bgColor="red">
                Column 3
              </GridItem>
            </Grid>
          </Box>
        </Flex>
      </Flex>
    </ChakraProvider>
  );
}

export default App;
